        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3216409027" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13610585573027960559">I enjoyed listening to the audio version of this book. It was given to me by the author in return for an honest review. It is a collection of short stories and poems that are written from a male perspective. The writing is very descriptive and full of emotion. The metaphors really bring the writing to life. I especially enjoyed the story ‘lady bug’. It really made me think. This book was a refreshing, thought provoking read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


